Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after Shirahoshi,\N are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves\N caught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:11.85,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Sun Pirates Split! Jimbei vs. Arlong!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so that was how the captain of \Nthe Sun Pirates - Fisher Tiger died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you all must know \Nhow painful it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the crew who were left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't kill humans"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See what happens when \Nyou show mercy to them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Tai was a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive them at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Fish-Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Arlong, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you here?\N Why did you come back so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:25.15,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}THE NAVY HQ VICE ADMIRAL\NBORSALINO (FUTURE ADMIRAL KIZARU)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...nonchalantly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill all the people \Nwho betrayed Big Brother Tai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to that island too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're seeking revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Fisher Tiger is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lowly creatures killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I see, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you need to come with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enraged by Fisher Tiger's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong lashed out against \Nhumans and he was imprisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He could've survived if he hadn't\N been refused a transfusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fisher Tiger didn't have to die \Nif there was Fish-Man's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You humans killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fisher Tiger, \Nthe Captain of the Sun Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dies After Being Denied a \NTransfusion of Human Blood."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too far from the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cause of his death was related to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong told the Navy a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth was far more tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger was betrayed by humans so he \Nrefused their blood because he had
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hard feelings against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, he was a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that became public, \Nit would have stained Boss' honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Arlong told a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Jimbei! There is an enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without the Boss,\N there is no turning back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare for action!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I start identifying myself as \N"First Son of the Sea" Jimbei
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and as the captain of the Sun Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did nothing but fight, day in and day out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:38.58,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}THE FISHMAN ISLAND - THE RYUGU PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.58,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"I am writing this because..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...I thought that you two deserved\N to know the whole truth."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Sun Pirates captain - Jimbei."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Tiger had no choice but\N to live the way he did-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:09:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I understand what was going\N through his mind that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be alright! I will not give in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall live under the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day that humans and we \Nunderstand each other will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign here to show that you want to relocate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible, Otohime-sama!\N We just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans refused to help \NTiger-san who saved slaves
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of all races without discrimination!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we understand them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another day without any signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sweet babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my consolation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a great future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime was working\N so hard day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rescuing humans from shipwrecks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you alright?!\N--It was pirates again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Help me...\N--Of course, we will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take them to the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teaching the island children\N about the world above...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:11:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I taught you yesterday, this is \Nan area with many trees called forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forest? The Sea Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Collecting signatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only take a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you folk are the ones \Nwho signed it, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many signatures have you got so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been doing this for 5 years
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but on about 100 sheets of paper\N there are 10 signatures each.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means there are 1000 supporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The population of the Fish-Man Island is \N5 million so, to be honest, I'd prefer more...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here is what we have to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're afraid we want to withdraw \Nour signatures - which amount to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about half of what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:11:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard yet? \NThe pirates who arrived the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...committed a robbery in this \Ntown and got away from the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh kids! Do you want to hear\N about the world above?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... My mom wants the paper \Nthat I signed the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom wants it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I listened to you because you're the Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have problems with humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't wanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hear your speech anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are tired of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked so hard today! I'm home, my angels!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I overdid it... \NCould you leave me alone for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are all liars!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama! You're on the air\N - the whole country heard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shurrup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minister of the Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you drunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shurrup! I'm not... I'm not drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is that?\N--Is that Otohime-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We... We are capable of staying \Nin the water forever if we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the ocean so broad,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and on the seafloor so dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we chose to live in this \Nlimited area... Do you know why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it because there is some light and air?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is more light above ground,\N and the sky is higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do our children sneak \Nout to see the Sabaody Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more beautiful places \Nthan we can imagine in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no place that we should not go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are just making convenient \Nexcuses to convince yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and giving everything up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And go for what you truly want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If humans stand in your way,\N let's face them together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe we can make a difference for \Nthe future of the children on this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even just a small one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left my family behind \Non the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My kid and wife... I wonder \Nhow they are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can go home someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We former slaves will get\N killed if they find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So whether we want it or not, we have to \Nkeep sailing for the rest of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I didn't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:35.74,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}THE NAVY HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that you got beaten so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong, who was locked up in Impel\N down the other day, is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most violent one is Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was unbelievably strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous to have him at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:12.07,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,UNCLEAR JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want me to join the Seven Warlords?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bounty was raised \Nto 250 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They figured that you're gonna be an \Neven bigger threat to the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They finally got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's turn them down and gain \Nmore notoriety, Captain Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think I'm gonna take the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Jimbei! \NI heard about the Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I join the Warlords, Aladdin and the\N others who don't want to be pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:19:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can live in this country without being \Nchased under the amnesty of the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, if I become a Warlord,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Fish-Man can get closer\N to the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the good of the Queen who \Nwe've caused so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not feeling well now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it could make the late \NTiger's dream come true -
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,liberation and freedom for the Fish-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the same time, I think the amnesty\N would cause us some trouble too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:41.91,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}IMPEL DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Arlong-san!\N--Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Arlong-san!\N--Arlong-san is back! He's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got something to say, just say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna join the Warlords,\N huh? Brother Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be the \NGovernment's dog, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember what Brother Tai said?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let resentment and \Nanger get the better of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten soft, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'd be safe if I just \Nfollowed you, but I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead the Arlong Pirates again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my men with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong, you fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really wanna stop\N me, you better kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Arlong-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do it, I'm free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I represent the anger of the Fish-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How arrogant you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take him away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two grew up together and\N he's like a brother to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you couldn't just kill \Nhim even though you were justified.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't that fool understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what Brother Tai truly meant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever he goes, as long as he engages\Nin violence, the Navy won't leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or if that doesn't work,\N let's go and stop him ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, we'll go our own way,\N just like we used to, Captain Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Macro, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, he's like a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sun Pirates split into three groups
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and went separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Jimbei's status \Nas one of the Seven Warlords,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.37,0:23:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he is able to safely bring the \Nformer slave Fish-Men home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Otohime's ideal future \Nhad seemed one step closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a drifting ship arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On board is a Celestial Dragon \Nwho thinks of Fish-Men as
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing more than slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shaking Fish-Man Island! \NA Celestial Dragon Drifts In!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
